description: A man carrying a briefcase walks past a picket fence towards a house. On the fence is a sign warning of a dog. Behind the fence, next to the house and partially hidden by a large tree, is a tank. Inside the open hatch of the tank, a dog is sitting, looking out. This creates a humorous and absurd situation where the typical warning about a dog is drastically subverted by the dog's unusual mode of guarding.
